Adapted LOOMIER areas
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following LOOMIER runtime/test areas are informed by the copied Rapier
examples, but are implemented as LOOMIER-owned TypeScript against the official
`@dimforge/rapier3d-compat` package:

  GAME_ENGINE/src/physics/RapierExampleFixtures.ts
    adapts fixture patterns from character_controller3.rs,
    character_controller2.rs, sensor3.rs, collision_groups3.rs, and
    stress_tests/ray_cast3.rs.

  GAME_ENGINE/tests/physics-rapier-source-adoption.test.ts
    verifies the adapted fixtures against LOOMIER wrappers for character
    controller, named collision layers, sensors, ray casting, and debug render.

No Rapier core engine internals, solver code, broad phase, narrow phase,
geometry pipeline, crate build setup, or Rust/WASM bindings are used as
LOOMIER runtime code in this phase.

No Rapier assets are copied in this phase.
